    public class RemoteQBusImpl
extends PVBusLimitImpl
implements RemoteQBus
    An implementation of the model object 'Remote QBus'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Remote QControl Type
    • Flow From2 To
    • Mvar On From Side
    • DQ dv
    • Acc Factor
    • Mvar Specified
    • Remote Bus Branch Id
    • Remote Bus
    • Remote Branch
